  },
  {
    question: "How does the AI handle F-Gas regulation queries?",
    answer: "The AI doesn't discuss F-Gas regulations, certification, or compliance requirements with callers. Those are technical and regulatory conversations that need to happen between you and the client directly. The AI focuses on capturing the enquiry — what system, what work, and when — and sends it to you with full details. You handle the compliance discussion as part of your quoting process."
